sentences: He started out playing drums and bass, but switched to keyboards after graduating from high school in 1987.
He was initiated at Alpha Epsilon Chapter at North Carolina Central University in Spring 1988.
In 2015, he began a new music project called Lewis City alongside British house and garage producer Danny J Lewis.
In 2017, he released his house music inspired second album The Feel Good Agenda, Vol. 1.
